<plot>Hannibal &amp; Manuel, two Latinos, manage to cross the US Border illegally from Mexico through the Desert. After running out of food and water, they finally find a lonely Trailer with some food &amp; drinks, but also with a passed out old man. Hannibal wants to get help for the man, but Manuel definitely don't want to risk getting caught and sent back to Mexico.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?079715</url></doc>
